      "id": "PopularPost104773",
      "post_content": "While I agree that this card does scream blue. I have to disagree that every blue deck should run this. Most blue decks would run [ponder](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=ponder) as a 1 drop instead of this. I personaly love this card as far as flavor is concerned. The concept is cool, simply pay ![Blue](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=U&type=symbol) and then for the rest of the game you know all the moves your opponents can make...unfourtantly in very quick serious games simply knowing what your opponent can do is usally worse than being able to do somthing yourself.\n  \n   ",
